For an example of how to catch rename events in workflows take a look at EventListing 

I think it's just the index page, the recent posts component and the blog archive (there may be others, look at what gets published on addition or deleting of a blog post in the same workflow)
http://www.london2012.com/blog/index.php

I think you need to do this in JS so something like this (don't just past the below in verbatim as I haven't tested it!)
var blogIndex = Page.get(/blog/index.php);
blogIndex.publish();

var blogPromo = Page.get(/blog/promo.php);
blogPromo.publish();
